Package: rules
Title: Model Wrappers for Rule-Based Models
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Max", "Kuhn", , "max@rstudio.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2402-136X")),
    person("RStudio", role = "cph")
  )
Description: Bindings for additional models for use with the 'parsnip'
    package.  Models include prediction rule ensembles (Friedman and
    Popescu, 2008) <doi:10.1214/07-AOAS148>, C5.0 rules (Quinlan, 1992
    ISBN: 1558602380), and Cubist (Kuhn and Johnson, 2013)
    <doi:10.1007/978-1-4614-6849-3>.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/tidymodels/rules,
    https://rules.tidymodels.org/
Depends: 
    modeldata,
    parsnip (>= 0.2.0)
Imports: 
    dials,
    dplyr,
    generics (>= 0.1.0),
    purrr,
    rlang,
    stringr,
    tibble,
    tidyr
Suggests: 
    C50,
    covr,
    Cubist,
    knitr,
    recipes,
    rmarkdown,
    spelling,
    testthat,
    xrf (>= 0.2.0)
Config/Needs/website:
    tidyr, 
